title: Turn On The Jets
description:
The Mina Kimes Show featuring Lenny: Mina Kimes and Domonique Foxworth recap Monday Night Football between the Chargers and Broncos. Are we being too hard on Russell Wilson? Plus, they give their Winners & Woofs for Week 6, including surprising performances by the Jets and Giants defensive lines, and the Vikings - who are now 5-1. But what’s going on with Tom Brady and the Buccaneers? They might still be okay in the NFC, but the Cardinals offense is in serious trouble.
